<h1 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #f8fafc; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
  Welcome aboard, <%= @user.name.presence || "there" %>!
</h1>

<p style="margin-bottom: 18px; color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.82);">
  Thanks for joining Jotchain. You now have a focused workspace for logging quick wins and getting meeting-ready summaries delivered automatically.
</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 18px 20px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(15, 24, 40, 0.78); border: 1px solid rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.18);">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.9); font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;">
    Here&apos;s how to make the most of your 14-day trial:
  </p>
  <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.82); line-height: 1.6;">
    <li><strong>Log your first note today:</strong> Capture a quick win or blocker so tomorrow&apos;s summary has context.</li>
    <li><strong>Schedule your digests:</strong> Create notifications for stand-ups, weeklies, or project reviews so emails land right before the meeting.</li>
    <li><strong>Skim the dashboard:</strong> Track your streak, review previous entries, and keep work organized with optional tags.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<%= render "mailers/shared/button", url: dashboard_url, label: "Open Jotchain" %>

<p style="margin-top: 24px; color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.85); font-size: 14px;">
  Need a hand getting set up? Just reply to this email and we&apos;ll help you out.
</p>
